#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.22"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.22:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.22:0.2"
msgid "3. Koṭigāmavagga "
msgstr "3. At the Village of Koṭi "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.22:0.3"
msgid "22. Dutiyakoṭigāmasutta "
msgstr "22. At the Village of Koṭi (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.22:1.1"
msgid "“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are ascetics and brahmins who don’t truly understand about suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "

msgctxt "sn56.22:1.2"
msgid "na me te, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu vā samaṇasammatā brāhmaṇesu vā brāhmaṇasammatā, na ca pana te āyasmanto sāmaññatthaṃ vā brahmaññatthaṃ vā diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharanti. "
msgstr "I don’t regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables don’t realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and don’t live having realized it with their own insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.433, sc2
msgctxt "sn56.22:2.1"
msgid "Ye ca kho keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, "
msgstr "There are ascetics and brahmins who do truly understand about suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "

msgctxt "sn56.22:2.2"
msgid "te kho me, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu ceva samaṇasammatā brāhmaṇesu ca brāhmaṇasammatā, te ca panāyasmanto sāmaññatthañca brahmaññatthañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharantī”ti. "
msgstr "I regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and live having realized it with their own insight.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.22:3.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn56.22:3.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn56.22:4.1"
msgid "“Ye dukkhaṃ nappajānanti, "
msgstr "“There are those who don’t understand suffering "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:4.2"
msgid "atho dukkhassa sambhavaṃ; "
msgstr "and suffering’s cause, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:4.3"
msgid "Yattha ca sabbaso dukkhaṃ, "
msgstr "and where all suffering "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:4.4"
msgid "asesaṃ uparujjhati. "
msgstr "ceases with nothing left over. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn56.22:5.1"
msgid "Tañca maggaṃ na jānanti, "
msgstr "And they don’t know the path "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:5.2"
msgid "Dukkhūpasamagāminaṃ; "
msgstr "that leads to the stilling of suffering. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:5.3"
msgid "Cetovimuttihīnā te, "
msgstr "They lack the heart’s release, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:5.4"
msgid "Atho paññāvimuttiyā; "
msgstr "as well as the release by wisdom. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:5.5"
msgid "Abhabbā te antakiriyāya, "
msgstr "Unable to make an end, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:5.6"
msgid "Te ve jātijarūpagā. "
msgstr "they continue to be reborn and get old. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn56.22:6.1"
msgid "Ye ca dukkhaṃ pajānanti, "
msgstr "But there are those who understand suffering "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:6.2"
msgid "atho dukkhassa sambhavaṃ; "
msgstr "and suffering’s cause, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:6.3"
msgid "Yattha ca sabbaso dukkhaṃ, "
msgstr "and where all suffering "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:6.4"
msgid "asesaṃ uparujjhati. "
msgstr "ceases with nothing left over. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn56.22:7.1"
msgid "Tañca maggaṃ pajānanti, "
msgstr "And they understand the path "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:7.2"
msgid "dukkhūpasamagāminaṃ; "
msgstr "that leads to the stilling of suffering. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:7.3"
msgid "Cetovimuttisampannā, "
msgstr "They’re endowed with the heart’s release, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:7.4"
msgid "atho paññāvimuttiyā; "
msgstr "as well as the release by wisdom. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:7.5"
msgid "Bhabbā te antakiriyāya, "
msgstr "Able to make an end, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.22:7.6"
msgid "na te jātijarūpagā”ti. "
msgstr "they don’t continue to be reborn and get old.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.22:7.7"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
